    <script type="text/javascript">
        function changeMap(lat, lng) {
            document.getElementById("ctl00_cphBody_hLat").value = lat;
            document.getElementById("ctl00_cphBody_hLng").value = lng;
            initialize();
        }

        function initialize() {
            var lat = document.getElementById("ctl00_cphBody_hLat").value;
            var lng = document.getElementById("ctl00_cphBody_hLng").value;
            if (lat.replace(' ', '') != "") {
                var map = new GMap2(document.getElementById("map_canvas"));
                map.setCenter(new GLatLng(lat, lng), 15);
                map.addControl(new GSmallMapControl());


                var point;
                point = new GLatLng(lat, lng);
                var marker;
                marker = new GMarker(point);
                map.addOverlay(marker);
            }
        }
            
    </script>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        var tt = document.getElementById("ctl00_cphBody_remaining");
        if (tt != null) {
            var spl = tt.innerHTML.split(':');
            var hh = parseInt(spl[0]);
            var mm = parseInt(spl[1]);
            var ss = parseInt(spl[2]);
            var refreshIntervalId = setInterval("updateClock()", 1000);

        }
        function updateClock() {
            var str;
            ss = ss - 1;
            if (ss == -1) {
                ss = 59;
                mm = mm - 1;
                if (mm == -1) {
                    mm = 59;
                    hh = hh - 1;
                    if (hh == -1) {
                        hh = 0;
                        mm = 0;
                        ss = 0;
                        clearInterval(refreshIntervalId);
                        tt.innerHTML = "Expired";
                    }
                }
            }
            str = hh.toString() + ":";
            if (mm.toString().length == 1)
                str += "0" + mm.toString() + ":";
